  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Ensure all fonts are loaded properly via Google Fonts (Clash Display, IBM Plex Sans).",
    "Use Shadcn UI components extensively for the dashboard but strip out heavy shadows and rounded corners (use rounded-sm).",
    "Implement a clear F-Pattern for the dashboard using a collapsible left sidebar.",
    "For the marketing page, use generous padding (py-24, py-32) and the 'Tetris Grid' pattern for features.",
    "Always apply data-testid to interactive elements."
  ]
